snippet.title: Pawarumi Launch Trailer : January 30th, 2018!
snippet.description:
Pawarumi is now ready to be enjoyed by everyone! 
Starting 30th of January, prepare yourself to confront the Neo Aztec Apocalypse on Steam !
Buy it now! http://store.steampowered.com/app/610410/PAWARUMI/
Discover more on http://www.pawarumi.com
